{
  "stem": "1901.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He was in Auschwitz-- in Monowitz is-- is an Aussenlager-- he was there, but he couldn't-- he had no contact with the outside world.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He-- I met him quite a few times after, because I was with my aunt.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "She took him straightaway home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I lost contact with him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He's also an old man now, like me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But amazing that a boy-- a Jewish boy-- he was protect-- he was circumcised, and he told, and the other boys protected him always, when he had to shower.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "You know, because the-- but he came right through the war.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And in Monowitz, the cruelty.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "The-- I had a friend working with me, and he was hated.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "The boy was so strong that he was hated by the kapos because he was so strong.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "He was-- and-- and-- you know, some boys look strong.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "You know, he had muscles and arms, and they always really went against him.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And one day, we have to carry [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] things from the barrack, from one to the other one, and that kapo-- a Polish kapo-- hit him, the friend of mine.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I call him friend because we shared everything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "He hit, and he lost his temper and gave him a-- a-- and gave him a smack in his face.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "He was very strong.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Normally, if you hit a kapo, that's the end of it, but we had an SS man walking with us.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "He said, oh, oh!",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Oh.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Start fighting.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Sadist.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And they had to fight.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And it was also strong man, and that-- that friend of mine hit the man that much he finished up in-- in hospital.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I'd never seen him back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I don't know if he died.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "I've never seen him, anyway.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "But they were so sadistic.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
